results.title: The Sprudge Guide To Coffee In Louisville, Kentucky
results.snippet: Now with seven locations, Quills Coffee is synonymous with the Louisville specialty coffee scene. It is important to the company to build relationships with coffee producers and source beans in a sustainable way. The menu at Quills ranges from the familiar to the exciting. Some of the signature drinks include an espresso sour and a coffee soda. The summer menu featured a churro latte and refreshing virgin cocktails.
